    <body>
        <%- include('partials/header') %>
        <div class="container-fluid about-top">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row text-center top-row">
                    <div class="col-sm-12">
                                              
                        <h1 class="fs-1 page-head h-2">LEAVE A TIP</h1>

                    </div>                    
                </div>             
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row text-center row-tips">
                    <div class="col-sm-12">
                        <h2 class="fs-2">See something? Say something - Anonymously!</h2>
                        <p class=" fs-4 row-tips">Have you ever witnessed something suspicious or felt uneasy about an activity in your neighborhood, but hesitated to speak up? 
                            Your watchful eyes can make a difference! Our local police department values and encourages your input.</p>
                    </div>

                </div>
                <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-lg-2 g-4 align-items-center text-md-center text-lg-start">
                                  
                    <div class="col">
                      <div class="card">
                         <div class="card-body">
                            <ol class=" fs-5">
                                <li>üïµÔ∏è‚Äç‚ôÇÔ∏è Accuracy</li>
                                <p>The information provided should be as accurate as possible. 
                                    Mistaken or misleading tips can divert valuable resources and may harm innocent individuals.
                                </p>
                                <li>ü§ê Specific Details</li>
                                <p>The tip should include specific details such as names, locations, dates, and any other relevant information.
                                     Specifics help law enforcement investigate and act more efficiently.
                                </p>
                                <li>üë• Credibility</li>
                                <p>The credibility of the source is important. 
                                    Tips from reliable and trustworthy individuals are more likely to be taken seriously by law enforcement.
                                </p>
                                <li>üåê Timeliness & Context</li>
                                <p>Tips that are timely and current provide law enforcement with a better chance of preventing.
                                    Understanding the circumstances or motivations behind the tip can assist law enforcement in assessing its significance.
                                </p>
                            </ol>
                        </div>
                      </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col">
                      <div class="card">
                        <img src="/images/tip.png" class="card-img-top img-fluid" alt="Police officer icon.">
                        
                      </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <hr>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="container">
                <div class="row align-items-center text-center row-tips col-div">
                    <div class="col-sm-12">
                        <h2 class="fs-2">Leave Anonymously!</h2>
                        <p class=" fs-4 row-tips">Does it feel like the situation could get heated or violent very soon? 
                            Is someone in immediate danger? Do you need support right away? If so, please call <a href="Tel:911">911</a> now.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row align-items-center text-center row-tips">
                        <div class="col-sm-3">

                        </div>
                        <div class="col-sm-6">
                            <form action="/submit" class=" "></form>
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <label for="exampleDataList" class="form-label fs-4">Search Crime Category</label>
                                    <input class="form-control" list="datalistOptions" id="exampleDataList" placeholder="Type to search...">
                                    <datalist id="datalistOptions">
                                    <option value="Crime">
                                    <option value="Terrorism">
                                    <option value="Corruption">
                                    <option value="Corporate Embezzlement">
                                    <option value="Murder">
                                    </datalist>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <label for="exampleFormControlTextarea1" class="form-label fs-4">Enter Detailed Description of the Crime You're Reporting</label>
                                    <textarea class="form-control" id="exampleFormControlTextarea1" rows="3"></textarea>
                                </div>
                                <div class="mb-3">
                                    <label for="formFileMultiple" class="form-label fs-4">Have some Documents? Attatch multiple files here</label>
                                    <input class="form-control" type="file" id="formFileMultiple" multiple>
                                </div>
                                
                                <button type="submit" class="btn btn-outline-warning btn-lg site-btn">
                                    Submit <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-right"></i>
                                </button>
                            </form>

                        </div>
                        
                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>


       
        




